Version 1.0.5 - Not released yet!

Version 1.0.4 - 15/06/2013
 - Minor fixes to code style & documentation.

Version 1.0.3 - 07/05/2013
 - Fix getopt errors running with RHEL5.
 - Set permissions on certs & keys in store if they look wrong.
 - Added safer --fetch option which will only automate fetching certs.
 - Use different fields in CA interface to get cert as old method will
   stop working next week.

Version 1.0.2 - 01/05/2013
 - Ensure private key is in PKCS#1 format.
 - Set cert permissions 0644 for simplicity.

Version 1.0.1 - 01/05/2013
 - Added batch option.
 - Minor improvements.

Version 1.0.0 - 26/04/2013
 - Initial version.

